{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/SRLibraryHeroDesc.png?t=1737921079\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STRAP IN, PILOT!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have one goal: Annihilate as many waves as you can! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are the pilot of the <strong>SANDRIPPER</strong>, a <strong>dual-wielding hover tank.</strong> Push your<strong> nuclear engine</strong> to its melting point as you <strong>rip</strong> through wave after wave of a ruthless planetary invasion force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/weaponShowcase-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1737921079\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPERIMENTAL FUN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Randomized waves, upgrades, and a partially destructible map create unpredictability to take advantage of. Unlock <strong>MULTI-FUNCTION</strong> weapons to pair with upgrades and create the perfect annihilation machine.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even your <strong>ENGINE</strong> is a weapon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/dumpShowcase-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1737921079\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TWO DIFFERENT GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ENDLESS MODE:</strong> Each day has a new leaderboard, and a new chance to see how far you can go! Highly random and highly chaotic. Classic wave survival gameplay with boss fights and upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WEEKLY SEEDED MODE:</strong> If you don't fancy randomness, every week a shared run is generated for all players. A crazy predetermined sequence of events with its own leaderboard to climb!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/t-ezgif.com-optimize_1_.gif?t=1737921079\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TRY, DIE, REPEAT.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Hone your skills, unlock weapons, and discover new strategies with each 5-10 minute long attempt. Gradually increasing your capabilities until you become a <strong>master of obliteration</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/SRSteamImage1.png?t=1737921079\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737921079","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/page.bg.jpg?t=1737921079","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737921079","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737921079","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3106900,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619040/extras/SRLibraryHeroDesc.png?t=1737921079\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STRAP IN, PILOT!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have one goal: Annihilate as many waves as you can! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are the pilot of the <strong>SANDRIPPER</strong>, a <strong>dual-wielding hover tank.</strong> Push your<strong> nuclear engine</strong> to its m